Description: code_saturne is a free, open-source CFD software developed primarily by EDF, designed to solve the Navier-Stokes equations for 2D, 2D-axisymmetric, and 3D flows, steady or unsteady, laminar or turbulent, incompressible or weakly compressible.
Home Page: https://www.code-saturne.org
Programs: code_saturne
